&lt;p&gt;Disturbed surfaces to be made good to match&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
The new rear UGF to LGF balustrade shall match the existing balustrade in terms of materials,
proportions, details, finish and colour.
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: To ensure that special regard is paid to protecting the special architectural and historic
interest and integrity of the building.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
